{
  "stem": "24466.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always, letters are written when I was advancing him with some money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The money, when you are asking me where from, they came, they come from-- from that to shut me up, my mouth-- from the money what I was getting from them, from the Pikoris.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that-- what I was doing, that I brought this out from my home, from my father, to help people, not to live for yourself, but to think about others too.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lvowicz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was no mail list.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only letters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had his own-- he was himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't know what will be, and just telling who was-- what I was doing to him and how he could leave, that he could leave in such bad times, that he could leave.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these-- these notes weren't sent anywhere, though.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were kept as a record of the-- of the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A record what I was doing, actually-- writing about-- mostly, mostly writing about me, what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were getting news from people that they escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came, and they tell us what is going on there-- especially to contract what I've got, what I got more with my father, the correspondence what went through Poles.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Jews, being in ghetto in Radom, couldn't write.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It that correct?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The same thing applies to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a family in-- in Radom, Bolesta-- Bolesta.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Through them, letters were written to me, to a family in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can't recollect the-- the name of the-- the family in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Could you spell the Bolesta name, please?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-O-L-E-S-T-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because my father bring-- that was-- that wasn't in-- in the time when the war broke out already between-- that was before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm talking-- sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
